data.description:
Wonderfully maintained home with brand new roof, new paint, and granite counter tops throughout!

New roof 2019
New Professional Exterior Paint 2019
Granite countertops throughout
2 storage blgs. 
Argon filled windows installed 2014 throughout, including in both storage sheds
Trane HVAC system
Sprinkler system for full yard and flowerbeds
All appliances stay - SS kitchen Appliances
2 inch wood blinds throughout
Covered Patio plus extended patio w/ Hot tub
Large floored attic
Fully insulated oversize garage w/ heat and AC w/ workbench alcove (extended depth on one side will fit 20' boat plus another vehicle) w/ sink
2 1/2 car drive across from cul-de-sac
Across the street from a Starbucks!

No realtors at this time please
data.whatILove: The backyard for this home is absolutely wonderful! A large patio for plenty of outdoor seating is great for entertaining.  The offset location for our grill, a hot tub, trees and plenty of lighting make the backyard feel like an oasis.  My wife loves the granite counter tops, deep stainless steel single basin sink, and bar in the kitchen.  Double vanities with granite counter tops in both bathrooms are excellent.  Ample storage with enormous walk in closets (2 closets in the master)!! If that storage isn't enough, the attic is floored for tons of extra space.  The over sized garage has AC and heat (separate from the home HVAC).  It includes a garage sink and a workbench area.
